import React from 'react';
import { Button, Form, FormGroup, Label, Input, FormText } from 'reactstrap';

const addItem = (props) => {
    return (
      <Form >
      <FormGroup>
          <Label for="sector">Sector</Label>
          <Input type="text" name="sector" id="sector" placeholder="Enter a sector" />
        </FormGroup>
        <FormGroup>
          <Label for="governorate">Governorate</Label>
          <Input type="text" name="governorate" id="governorate" placeholder="Enter a governorate" />
        </FormGroup>
        <FormGroup>
          <Label for="maison_dhote">Maison d'hote</Label>
          <Input type="text" name="maison_dhote" id="maison_dhote" placeholder="Enter Your a Name" />
        </FormGroup>
        <FormGroup>
          <Label for="num">Password</Label>
          <Input type="number" name="num" id="num" placeholder="Enter a Number" />
        </FormGroup>
        <FormGroup>
          <Label for="email">Email</Label>
          <Input type="email" name="email" id="email" placeholder="Enter Your Email" />
        </FormGroup>
        <FormGroup>
          <Label for="website">Website</Label>
          <Input type="text" name="website" id="website" placeholder="Enter a website" />
        </FormGroup>
        <FormGroup>
          <Label for="image">Image</Label>
          <Input type="text" name="image" id="image" placeholder="Enter an image URL" />
        </FormGroup>
        
    <Button>Submit</Button>
    </Form>
    
    );
}

export default addItem;
